      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under version control with documented test suite covering relevant physics; all simulation scripts archived in institutional repository.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 is deployed under institutional software QA protocol SQA-CFD-004. Version control enforced via Git; regression test suite of 47 benchmark cases executed and archived. All simulation input files and post-processing scripts stored in read-only institutional repository with checksums verified."
