      "rationale": "Validation activities performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — the same geometric class as the COU device. Operating conditions match CPB clinical range. Blood analog (glycerol-water, 3.5 cP at 37°C) is standard for hemolysis testing per ASTM F1841. Validation scope is directly relevant to COU."
